title: MisterMusic Show 292 indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show - 292  (192 kbps MP3)


New Music on this week's show from Blackbird & The Storm, Cathedrals, Miamigo, and Maximo Park.


Plus a huge alternative rock hit is the 'Oldie of the Week'.  A song that spent 15 weeks on the top of the US modern rock charts in the winter of 1998.


It's a 2 hour mix of indie, alternative and rock classics. Broadcasting weekly and heard globally, it's the MisterMusic Show.





MisterMusic is featured on Rock XS Internet Radio (rockxs.com)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page http://mistermusicshow.com   Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search  mistermusicshow  (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
